  "title": "Marketing trainee (Entry level)",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Royal Org</strong></p><p>Royal Org is a fast-growing outsourced sales and marketing firm specialising in face-to-face marketing and revenue generation in Singapore.</p><p>We partner with clients across industries, including NGOs, lifestyle, energy, and FMCG, to boost brand awareness and drive measurable results.</p><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><p>• Clear career progression</p><p>• ⁠Supportive, dynamic, and ambitious team culture</p><p>• ⁠Comprehensive training and mentorship provided</p><p>• ⁠Team events and travel opportunities</p><p>• ⁠Weekly Payouts<br /><br />• Fun working environment (Different from your typical corporate office layouts and vibes!)<br /></p><p>• No experience needed</p><p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><p>• Represent major brands through in-person marketing campaigns</p><p>• ⁠Engage customers and build strong relationships</p><p>• ⁠Collaborate with your team to meet targets and grow together</p><p>At Royal Org, we value passion, professionalism, and potential. </p><p>If you’re driven to learn, grow, and achieve, apply now to start your career with us now!</p>",
